## Falsifiers

35 falsifiable claims across 5 dependency levels. Every claim has an explicit test that would break it.

	Level 5: Seed / Transfer
	    │
	Level 4: Human Substrate
	    │
	Level 3: Geometry
	    │
	Level 2: Engine
	    │
	Level 1: Ground Definitions
	
	Break Level 1 → everything falls
	Break Level 3 → Levels 1–2 stand, 3–5 fall
	Break Level 5 → Levels 1–4 stand, only Seed falls

The architecture is designed to degrade honestly. Full catalog: [`10_Master_Index_of_falsifiers.md`](10_Master_Index_of_falsifiers.md)

All 35 falsifiers are **Open**. The invitation to break them is permanent.

